title: This Is What Holds Us Back From Finding Love
description: In this episode, we breakdown dating and romantic relationships, and how to understand it from different perspectives as described in the Better Life Framework by the Co-x3 Family Foundation. This episode will help anyone struggling with dating in the modern world.

description: In this episode, we sit down with Maria, a professional woman in her early 30s, and help her feel less helpless with building own creative business selling mugs - while juggling a full time job, nurturing her relationship with her husband, starting a family, and moving to a new country.
author: Conrad Lin

title: 27 Year Old Woman Working In Big Tech Discovers Her Path To Self-Alignment
description: In this episode, we sit down with Sarah, a 27 year old woman working in a big tech company and discuss how to live a life that is aligned with her true self.
